      • CertificationDecision

        public CertificationDecision(CertificationItem item,
                             CertifiableDescriptor certifiableDesc)
        Deprecated. 
        Creates a decision record with the given item and certifiable. Useful in cases where the certifiable is not the primary entitlement being certified. For example - cases where the certifier has chosen to revoke the required and/or permitted roles for a given role. In that case the certifiableDesc will not match the role on the certification item.

        item -
        certifiableDesc -
